{
  "stem": "280.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The one where-- there was a main shul, which stands today-- a few years ago when I was there, it stands.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, it's practically in ruins.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you could see the-- the former glory of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the shul that we went to was another shul, not this main shul, where-- which was a large shul.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, here in Los Angeles, you could see a lot of Orthodox shuls, little rooms and things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was nothing of the sort.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a very nice shul.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was very nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the-- and the first floor was for the men and the upper floor for the women.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But a beautiful building, and built as a shul.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was a grain merchant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was in Satu Mare during the Austro-Hungarian rule.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jews were not allowed to live in the city proper.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They lived in provinces.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they-- then they-- you know, they were occupied with selling stuff, having little stores, and providing for the peasants things.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But only 100 years before we were deported, in the 1800s, when Franz Joseph-- who was a friend of the Jews-- allowed-- permitted the Jews to-- to move into Satu Mare.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the my father's family with four other families but among the first families who lived in the city proper.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was born under-- under the same address where my father was, only a different house-- my father built the house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that-- that place, that lot, was under the Feuer name over 100 years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The house?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, relatively, you know, to America standards, it was a small and modest house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was very-well built from brick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had four bedrooms.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had a big veranda, which had a-- a glass wall where we made the [INAUDIBLE] usually.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
